If you have shell access on the Kafka host, run exactly this for the one topic only:

```bash
./bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 \
  --group main-processor --describe
```

Then, if `click-stream` is the only topic you want to advance, run:

```bash
./bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 \
  --group main-processor \
  --topic click-stream \
  --reset-offsets --to-latest \
  --execute
```

And verify:

```bash
